name: MaternalAndFetalProcedures
title: Maternal and Fetal Procedures
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes representing maternal and fetal procedures.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients undergoing procedures related to pregnancy. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the "Procedure" category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes codes identifying maternal and fetal procedures, including delivery, obstetric, and fetal procedures.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes gynecological procedures that are not related to pregnancy.)
